Hi, I found a solution for those who have problem with the x64 patch. I believe it is caused by using a renamed installation path. To fix it, stop the "Diskeeper" service just in case, then copy all the files in C:/Program Files/Diskeeper Corporation/Diskeeper to your installed directory. After replace all the files, it should work.
